  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Upper Hand is a Deck-Building, Platformer that tests the players adaptability as Gen-0 ascends in pursuit of the parts required to rebuild his space ship, all to an original sound track.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <u><strong>Platforming</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embrace the art of bouldering as you climb ever higher clinging hand and foot to different holds. As you progress take into consideration unique environmental holds and learn the limitations of each one. Challenge yourself to improve and pursue new abilities and customized apparel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras/e6ad5937224d7046d85c453eb41e5c21.avif?t=1767407082\" width=900 height=472 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Adaptability</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience distinct biomes and adapt to their unique environmental challenges. Find freedom in the variety of possible solutions to each challenge. Carve your own path and pursue ever more efficient routes and times to score points to use in the shop. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras/295f693096916a3ba79152beabbbeb8b.poster.avif?t=1767407082\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras/295f693096916a3ba79152beabbbeb8b.webm?t=1767407082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras/295f693096916a3ba79152beabbbeb8b.mp4?t=1767407082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <u><strong>Deck</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Building Your future is in your hands as you craft your playstyle using a wide array of cards’ poses and abilities to quickly and successfully conquer each challenge. Using the points collected by accomplishing level achievements and spending them at the shop you can acquire new powers for gen-0 to use in his pursuit of the top.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras/45b3d3da478e9dc16c48fe52c1f33e2a.webp?t=1767407082\" width=48 height=71 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras/09e12ef5c5b3e40e6f8e9d3c9aaf25b3.webp?t=1767407082\" width=48 height=71 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras/33d1cd0dd14b6eb926846c5d92d89c6a.webp?t=1767407082\" width=48 height=71 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras/c93b32ae2b4e9c2c3c01ec5bd8600dcb.webp?t=1767407082\" width=48 height=71 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras/18e1573f3abe28adf8a1f660fff319ab.webp?t=1767407082\" width=48 height=71 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras/f8b26148667a541f3253852084161522.webp?t=1767407082\" width=48 height=71 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Gen-0</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gen-0 has been captured and needs your help! Gen-0 is Stuck in a foreign world and longs for home. Help him climb through different worlds to collect the parts of his ship needed to get back home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras/e52637daaa3605df3cbbbd702e79699b.avif?t=1767407082\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras_big/e52637daaa3605df3cbbbd702e79699b.webp?t=1767407082 width=1560 height=1560 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras/ff8185ac14f464102ab266f7583730ef.avif?t=1767407082\" width=64 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Music</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our original composer Ricky Hess has poured his heart and soul into our original soundtrack. It features elements of Jazz, City pop, synth-hop and a variety of other inspirations. The upbeat tracks are sure to invigorate your pursuit of the peak.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras/a42a99fbb5ec73a21c64ca54240a7c6c.avif?t=1767407082\" width=920 height=430 /></span></p>",
