gh different worlds to collect the parts of his ship needed to get back home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras/e52637daaa3605df3cbbbd702e79699b.avif?t=1767407082\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras_big/e52637daaa3605df3cbbbd702e79699b.webp?t=1767407082 width=1560 height=1560 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras/ff8185ac14f464102ab266f7583730ef.avif?t=1767407082\" width=64 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Music</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our original composer Ricky Hess has poured his heart and soul into our original soundtrack. It features elements of Jazz, City pop, synth-hop and a variety of other inspirations. The upbeat tracks are sure to invigorate your pursuit of the peak.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095030/extras/a42a99fbb5ec73a21c64ca54240a7c6c.avif?t=1767407082\" width=920 height=430 /></span></p>",
